							.panel-heading
								.panel-title
									a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapse1', aria-expanded="true").
										Who we are
							#collapse1.panel-collapse.collapse.in
								.panel-body
									p
										| We study business processes with our high tech BI team who are well aware in high tech trends and are able to cooperate on building solution architecture. Our cybersecurity specialists modify the designe to provide best security with desired flexibility and accessability for solution.
						.panel
							.panel-heading
								.panel-title
									a(data-toggle='collapse', data-parent='#accordion', href='#collapse2', aria-expanded="false").
										What we do
							#collapse2.panel-collapse.collapse
